&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The pattern followed is,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 1 &amp;rarr; 73 &amp;ndash; 21 &amp;rarr; 7 &amp;times; 3 = 21&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 2 &amp;rarr; 56 &amp;ndash; 30 &amp;rarr; 5 &amp;times; 6 = 30&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 3 &amp;rarr; 53 &amp;ndash; 15 &amp;rarr; 5 &amp;times; 3 = 15&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 4 &amp;rarr; 22 &amp;ndash; 6 &amp;rarr; 2 &amp;times; 2 = 4, not 6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;All follow the same pattern, except 22 &amp;ndash; 6.&lt;/p&gt;
Hence, &amp;ldquo;22 &amp;ndash; 6&amp;rdquo; is the odd number pair.<br><br><p style="">অনুসরণ করা প্যাটার্নটি হ'ল,</p>

<p style="">বিকল্প 1 &rarr; 73 - 21 &rarr; 7 &times; 3 = 21</p>

<p style="">বিকল্প 2 &rarr; 56 - 30 &rarr; 5 &times; 6 = 30</p>

<p style="">বিকল্প 3 &rarr; 53 - 15 &rarr; 5 &times; 3 = 15</p>

<p style=""><strong style="">বিকল্প 4 &rarr; 22 - 6 &rarr; 2 &times; 2 = 4, 6 নয়</strong></p>

<p style="">22 - 6 বাদে সকলেই একই প্যাটার্ন অনুসরণ করে।</p>
সুতরাং, "22 - 6" হল অমিল সংখ্যা্র জোড়।&nbsp;

&lt;p&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3241-5732&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 3241 -&amp;nbsp;5732 = -2491.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;2354-4835&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; 2354 - 4835 = -2481.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;1326-3807&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 1326 - 3807 =&amp;nbsp;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2481.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;2345-4826&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 2345 - 4826 =&amp;nbsp;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2481.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, &amp;#39;Option 1&amp;#39; is odd among the given options.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসরণ করা যুক্তিটি&nbsp;হল:</p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প</strong> 1<strong>)&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">3241-5732&nbsp;&rarr; 3241 -&nbsp;5732 = -2491.</span></strong></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 2)&nbsp;2354-4835&nbsp;&rarr; 2354 - 4835 = -2481.</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 3)&nbsp;1326-3807&nbsp;&rarr; 1326 - 3807 =&nbsp;-2481.</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 4)&nbsp;2345-4826&nbsp;&rarr; 2345 - 4826 =&nbsp;-2481.</span></p>

<p>সুতরাং, প্রদত্ত বিকল্পগুলির মধ্যে 'বিকল্প 1' হল অসম।</p>

<p>সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল <strong>"বিকল্প 1"&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>

&lt;p&gt;The logic follows here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pattern: Product of LHS = RHS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;457&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 4 &amp;times; 5 &amp;times; 7 = 140&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;925 &amp;rarr; 9 &amp;times; 2 &amp;times; 5 = 90&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;873 &amp;rarr; 8 &amp;times; 7 &amp;times; 3 = 168&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;568 &amp;rarr; 5 &amp;times; 6 &amp;times; 8 = 240 &amp;ne; 360&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As, all&amp;nbsp;the given options follow the same pattern except 568.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;568&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে যে&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">যুক্তি&nbsp;</span>অনুসরণ করা হয়:</p>

<p><strong>ধাঁচ: বামপক্ষ এর গুনফল = ডানপক্ষ&nbsp;</strong></p>

<p>457&nbsp;&rarr; 4 &times; 5 &times; 7 = 140</p>

<p>925 &rarr; 9 &times; 2 &times; 5 = 90</p>

<p>873 &rarr; 8 &times; 7 &times; 3 = 168</p>

<p><strong>568 &rarr; 5 &times; 6 &times; 8 = 240 &ne; 360</strong></p>

<p>যেমন, 568 ব্যতীত সমস্ত প্রদত্ত বিকল্প একই ধাঁচ&nbsp;অনুসরণ করে।</p>

<p>সুতরাং,<strong> "568" </strong>হল&nbsp;সঠিক উত্তর।&nbsp;</p>

&lt;p&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;168 &amp;ndash; 336&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 168&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 2 = 336&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;512 &amp;ndash; 1024&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 512&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 2 = 1024&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;358 &amp;ndash; 726&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 358&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 2 = 716&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;ne;&amp;nbsp;726&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;624 &amp;ndash; 1248&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 624&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 2 = 1248&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;358 &amp;ndash; 726&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসরণ করা যুক্তি হল:</p>

<p>1.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">168 &ndash; 336&nbsp;&rarr; 168&nbsp;</span><span style="  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&times; 2 = 336</span></p>

<p>2.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">512 &ndash; 1024&nbsp;&rarr; 512&nbsp;</span><span style="  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&times; 2 = 1024</span></p>

<p>3.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">358 &ndash; 726&nbsp;&rarr; 358&nbsp;</span><span style="  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&times; 2 = 716&nbsp;</span>&ne;&nbsp;726</p>

<p>4.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">624 &ndash; 1248&nbsp;&rarr; 624&nbsp;</span><span style="  background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&times; 2 = 1248</span></p>

<p>সুতরাং,<strong> '358 - 726'</strong> হল&nbsp;সঠিক উত্তর।&nbsp;</p>

&lt;p&gt;We consider the given options:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;55&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;∶&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;62&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;62 - 55 = 7&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;7 is a prime number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;64&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;∶&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;43&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;64 - 43 = 21&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;21 is not a prime number.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;83&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;∶&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;92&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;92 - 83 = 9&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;9 is not a prime number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;62&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;∶&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;71&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;71 - 62 = 9&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;9 is not a prime number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;55&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;∶&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;62 is the odd one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 1&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>আমরা প্রদত্ত বিকল্পগুলি বিবেচনা করি:</p>

<p>বিকল্প 1)&nbsp;<span style="">55&nbsp;</span><span style="">∶&nbsp;</span><span style="">62</span></p>

<p><span style="">62 - 55 = 7&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><strong><span style="">7 একটি মৌলিক সংখ্যা</span></strong></p>

<p><span style="">বিকল্প 2)&nbsp;64&nbsp;</span><span style="">∶&nbsp;</span><span style="">43&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="">64 - 43 = 21&nbsp;</span></p>

<p>21 একটি মৌলিক সংখ্যা নয়</p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প</span><span style=""> 3)&nbsp;83&nbsp;∶&nbsp;</span><span style="">92</span></p>

<p>92 - 83 = 9</p>

<p><span style="">9 </span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">একটি মৌলিক সংখ্যা নয়</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প</span><span style=""> 4)&nbsp;62&nbsp;∶&nbsp;</span><span style="">71&nbsp;</span></p>

<p>71 - 62 = 9&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="">9 </span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">একটি মৌলিক সংখ্যা নয়</span></p>

<p><span style="">অতএব,&nbsp;<strong>55&nbsp;</strong></span><strong><span style="">∶&nbsp;</span><span style="">62 হল বেমানান।</span></strong></p>

<p>সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর&nbsp;<strong>"বিকল্প 1"</strong></p>

&lt;p&gt;The pattern followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 1&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 16 :&amp;nbsp;82&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 4&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;, 9&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 49 :&amp;nbsp;65&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 7&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, 8&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 81 :&amp;nbsp;37&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 9&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, 6&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 16 :&amp;nbsp;48&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 4&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, 7&lt;span style=&quot;position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;1&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All follow the same pattern except &amp;quot;16 :&amp;nbsp;48&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;16 :&amp;nbsp;48&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the odd pair.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসৃত ধাঁচটি হল:</p>

<p>বিকল্প 1&nbsp;&rarr; 16 :&nbsp;82&nbsp;&rarr; 4<sup>2</sup>, 9<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;+ 1&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="">বিকল্প</span> 2&nbsp;&rarr; 49 :&nbsp;65&nbsp;&rarr; 7<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>, 8<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 1&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="">বিকল্প</span> 3&nbsp;&rarr; 81 :&nbsp;37&nbsp;&rarr; 9<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>, 6<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 1&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="">বিকল্প</span> 4&nbsp;&rarr; 16 :&nbsp;48&nbsp;&rarr; 4<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>, 7<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;1&nbsp;</strong></p>

<p>&quot;16 : 48&quot; ব্যতীত সবকটি একই ধাঁচ&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</p>

<p>সুতরাং, <strong>&quot;16 : 48&quot;</strong> হল বিষম&nbsp;জোড়া।</p>

&lt;p&gt;By checking options:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(1)&amp;nbsp;461 : 20&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 20&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 20 + 1 = 400 + 60&amp;nbsp; +1 = 461&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(2)&amp;nbsp;182 : 12&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 12&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 12 + 1 = 144 + 36 + 1 = 181&amp;nbsp;&amp;ne; 182&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(3)&amp;nbsp;305 : 16&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 16&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 16 + 1 = 256 + 48 + 1 = 305&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(4)&amp;nbsp;239 : 14&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 14&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 14 + 1 = 196 + 42 + 1 = 239&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;182 : 12&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the odd one.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>বিকল্পগুলি পরীক্ষা করে:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">(1)&nbsp;461 : 20&nbsp;&rarr; 20<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 3&nbsp;&times; 20 + 1 = 400 + 60&nbsp; +1 = 461</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">(2)&nbsp;182 : 12&nbsp;&rarr; 12<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 3&nbsp;&times; 12 + 1 = 144 + 36 + 1 = 181&nbsp;&ne; 182</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">(3)&nbsp;305 : 16&nbsp;&rarr; 16<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 3&nbsp;&times; 16 + 1 = 256 + 48 + 1 = 305</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">(4)&nbsp;239 : 14&nbsp;&rarr; 14<span style="position: relative;  line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 3&nbsp;&times; 14 + 1 = 196 + 42 + 1 = 239</p>

<p>অতএব, <span style="font-weight: 700;">182 : 12</span> হল বিজোড় সংখ্যা।</p>

&lt;p&gt;The logic is here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[(2&lt;sup&gt;nd&lt;/sup&gt; number)&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (2&lt;sup&gt;nd&lt;/sup&gt; number + 3)] + 1 = 1st number.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, follow the logic:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option (1):&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;181&amp;nbsp;∶ 12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[12&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (12 + 3)] + 1 = 12 &amp;times; 15 + 1 = 180 + 1= 181 = 1st number.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option (2):&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;271&amp;nbsp;∶ 15&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (15 + 3)] + 1 = 15 &amp;times; 18 + 1 = 270 + 1= 271 = 1st number.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option (3):&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;305&amp;nbsp;∶ 16&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[16&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (16 + 3)] + 1 = 16 &amp;times; 19 + 1 = 304 + 1= 305 = 1st number.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option (4):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;398&amp;nbsp;∶ 18&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Now, follow the logic:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[18&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (18 + 3)] + 1 = 18 &amp;times; 21 + 1 = 378 + 1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;= 379&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ne;&amp;nbsp;1st number.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This option do not follow the pattern.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, pair&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;398&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;∶&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; 18&lt;strong&gt;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is an odd one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/alternate-methord-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Alternate Method&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;LOGIC: (Second Number + 1)&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ Second Number = First Number&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Option (1):&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;181&amp;nbsp;∶ 12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;13&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 12&amp;nbsp;= 169 + 12&amp;nbsp;= 181&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Option (2):&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;271&amp;nbsp;∶ 15&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;16&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 15 = 256 + 15 = 271&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Option (3):&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;305&amp;nbsp;∶ 16&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;17&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 16 = 289 + 16 = 305&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;This option follows the pattern.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Option (4):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;398&amp;nbsp;∶ 18&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Now, follow the logic:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;19&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 18 = 379&amp;nbsp;&amp;ne; 398&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;This option do not follow the pattern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, pair&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;398&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;∶&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;18&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is an odd one.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><span style="">এখানে&nbsp;</span>যুক্তিটি হল নিম্নরূপ:</p>

<p>[(দ্বিতীয় সংখ্যা) &times; (<span style="">দ্বিতী</span><span style="">য়</span> সংখ্যা + 3)] + 1 = প্রথম সংখ্যা।</p>

<p>এখন, যুক্তিটি অনুসরণ করার পর:</p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (1):</strong> 181 ∶ 12</p>

<p>[12 &times; (12 + 3)] + 1 = 12 &times; 15 + 1 = 180 + 1 = 181 = প্রথম সংখ্যা।</p>

<p>এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (2):</strong> 271 ∶ 15</p>

<p>[15 &times; (15 + 3)] + 1 = 15 &times; 18 + 1 = 270 + 1 = 271 = <span style="">প্রথ</span><span style="">ম সংখ্যা</span>।</p>

<p><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</span></p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (3):</strong> 305 ∶ 16</p>

<p>[16 &times; (16 + 3)] + 1 = 16 &times; 19 + 1 = 304 + 1 = 305 = <span style="">প্রথ</span><span style="">ম সংখ্যা</span>।</p>

<p><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</span></p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (4):</strong> 398 ∶ 18</p>

<p><strong>এখন, যুক্তিটি অনুসরণ করার পর:</strong></p>

<p><strong>[18 &times; (18 + 3)] + 1 = 18 &times; 21 + 1 = 378 + 1= 379 &ne; <span style="">প্রথ</span><span style="">ম সংখ্যা</span>।</strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে</span>&nbsp;না।</strong></p>

<p>সুতরাং, <strong>"398 ∶ 18"</strong> জোড়াটি হল একটি বিষম জোড়া।</p>

<p><br />
<img height="26px" src="//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/alternate-methord-image.png" style="" width="26px" /><span style="font-size:22px;"><u style=" font-weight: 700; ">Alternate Method</u></span><br />
যুক্তি: (দ্বিতীয় সংখ্যা + <span style="">1)</span><span style=" line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; font-size:10.5px;">2</span> + দ্বিতীয় সংখ্যা = প্রথম সংখ্যা</p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (1):</strong> 181 ∶ 12</p>

<p>132 + 12 = 169 + 12 = 181</p>

<p><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</span></p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (2):</strong> 271 ∶ 15</p>

<p>162 + 15 = 256 + 15 = 271</p>

<p><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</span></p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (3):</strong> 305 ∶ 16</p>

<p>172 + 16 = 289 + 16 = 305</p>

<p><span style="">এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটি</span><span style="">&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে।</span></p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প (4):</strong> 398 ∶ 18</p>

<p><strong>এখন, যুক্তিটি অনুসরণ করার পর:</strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-weight: 700; ">19<span style=" line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;font-size:10.5px;">2</span>&nbsp;+ 18 = 379&nbsp;&ne; 398</span></strong></p>

<p><strong>এই বিকল্পটি ধাঁচটিকে&nbsp;অনুসরণ করছে&nbsp;না।</strong></p>

<p><span style="">সুতরাং,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: 700; ">"398 ∶ 18"</span><span style="">&nbsp;জোড়াটি হল একটি বিষম জোড়া।</span></p>

&lt;p&gt;The logic is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First number&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 13 = Second number&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. 8 : 104&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 8&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 13 = 104&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. 12 : 146&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 12&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 13 = 156&amp;nbsp;&amp;ne; 146&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. 5 : 65&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 5&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 13 = 65&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. 11 : 143&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 11&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 13 = 143&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;12 : 146&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo; is the odd one out.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>যুক্তিটি হলো:</p>

<p><strong>প্রথম সংখ্যা </strong><span style="font-weight: bolder;">&times;&nbsp;</span><strong>13 = দ্বিতীয় সংখ্যা</strong></p>

<p>1. 8 : 104 &rarr; 8 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&times;&nbsp;</span>13 = 104</p>

<p>2. 12 : 146 &rarr; 12 &times;&nbsp;13 = 156 &ne; 146</p>

<p>3. 5 : 65 &rarr; 5 <span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">&times;&nbsp;</span>13 = 65</p>

<p>4. 11 : 143 &rarr; 11 &times;&nbsp;13 = 143</p>

<p>সুতরাং, &lsquo;<strong>12 : 146</strong>&rsquo; হলো ভিন্ন।</p>

&lt;p&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Option 1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;3846 &amp;ndash; 4856 = -1010&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 2)&amp;nbsp;4892 &amp;ndash; 5902 = -1010&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 3)&amp;nbsp;4328 &amp;ndash; 5348 = -1020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Option 4)&amp;nbsp;3264 &amp;ndash; 4274 = -1010&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, &amp;#39;Option 3&amp;quot; is odd among the given option.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/mistake-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Mistake Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;In the options, you have given pairs and you need to find the difference of the numbers given. All the pairs would have similar difference except the one which is option 3rd.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, option 3rd will be the correct answer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসরণ করা যুক্তি হল:</p>

<p>বিকল্প 1)&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">3846 &ndash; 4856 = -1010</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 2)&nbsp;4892 &ndash; 5902 = -1010</span></p>

<p><strong><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 3)&nbsp;4328 &ndash; 5348 = -1020</span></strong></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">বিকল্প 4)&nbsp;3264 &ndash; 4274 = -1010</span></p>

<p>সুতরাং, প্রদত্ত বিকল্পের মধ্যে 'বিকল্প 3" হল বিষম।</p>

<p>সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল <strong>"বিকল্প 3"</strong>।</p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here the given logic is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;9&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 2 = 4.5 + .5 = 5&amp;nbsp;&amp;rArr; 5&lt;sup&gt;3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;= 125&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 2 = 5.5 + .5 = 6&amp;nbsp;&amp;rArr; 6&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= &lt;u&gt;216&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;13 &amp;divide; 2 = 6.5 + .5 = 7&amp;nbsp;&amp;rArr; 7&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 343&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;7 &amp;divide; 2 = 3.5 + .5 = 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rArr; 4&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As per the given logic, the &lt;strong&gt;correct answer is option 2,&lt;/strong&gt; as &lt;strong&gt;11 : 49 &lt;/strong&gt;do not follow the pattern that other options do.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p><strong>এখানে প্রদত্ত যুক্তি হল:</strong></p>

<p>9 &divide; 2 = 4.5 + .5 = 5 &rArr; 5<sup>3</sup> = 125</p>

<p><strong>11 &divide; 2 = 5.5 + .5 = 6 &rArr; 6<sup>3</sup> = <u>216</u></strong></p>

<p>13 &divide; 2 = 6.5 + .5 = 7 &rArr; 7<sup>3</sup> = 343</p>

<p>7 &divide; 2 = 3.5 + .5 = 4 &rArr; 4<sup>3</sup> = 64</p>

<p>প্রদত্ত যুক্তি অনুসারে, <strong>সঠিক উত্তর হল বিকল্প 2,</strong> যেহেতু&nbsp;<strong>11 : 49</strong> অন্যান্য বিকল্পগুলির মতো একই নিয়ম অনুসরণ করে না।</p>

questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Four of the following five figures are alike in a certain way and thus form a group. Which figure DOES NOT belong to that group?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2054.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><p>নিম্নলিখিত পাঁচটি চিত্রের মধ্যে চারটি একটি নির্দিষ্ট উপায়ে একই রকম এবং একটি দল তৈরি করে। কোন চিত্রটি সেই দলের অন্তর্গত নয়?</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2054.png" style="height: 127px; width: 500px;" /></p>

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Figure A)&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2056.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 120px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Figure is shown at a different angle of rotation in either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;clockwise or anticlockwise direction of the same figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Figure B&lt;/span&gt;)&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2055.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 120px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Figure is NOT shown at a different angle of rotation in either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;clockwise or anticlockwise direction of the same figure because the the circle at the corner instead of the side of the rectangle and the triangle is at the side instead at the corner of the rectangle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Figure C&lt;/span&gt;)&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2057.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 120px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Figure is shown at a different angle of rotation in either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;clockwise or anticlockwise direction of the same figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Figure D&lt;/span&gt;)&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2058.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 120px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Figure is shown at a different angle of rotation in either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;clockwise or anticlockwise direction of the same figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Figure E)&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/25/05/IMG%20-875%20%2007-05-25%20%20%20Yuvraj%20kori%2059.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 120px; height: 120px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Figure is shown at a different angle of rotation in either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;clockwise or anticlockwise direction of the same figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Thus, out of all the options &amp;#39;figure B&amp;#39; is the odd one out.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Option 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">এখানে অনুসৃত যুক্তি হল:</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">চিত্র A) <img alt="" src="//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage677e04db47821efa4c3ffb12.png" />&rArr; <span style="font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);">চিত্রটি একই চিত্রের ঘড়ির কাঁটার দিকে বা বিপরীত দিকে ঘূর্ণনের বিভিন্ন কোণে দেখানো হয়েছে।</span></p>

