questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;There are two straight lines and one heart shape element present&amp;nbsp;in the given figure.&lt;/p&gt;

