&lt;p&gt;Select the odd one&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-ade90ce0-7fff-3db3-efda-b79a0a773d36&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:500px;height:157px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D16.png&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 317px; height: 103px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><p>নিম্নলিখিত যেটি পৃথক, সেটি নির্বাচন করুন:-​</p>

<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-ade90ce0-7fff-3db3-efda-b79a0a773d36"><span style="  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:500px;height:157px;"><img src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D16.png" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 317px; height: 103px;" /></span></span></span></p>

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D17.png&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 81px; height: 100px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D18.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 27px; height: 21px;&quot; /&gt;Flowers are made on the side of figure.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D19.png&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 81px; height: 100px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D20.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 32px; height: 20px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Flowers are made on the side of figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D21.png&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 81px; height: 100px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D22.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 21px; height: 21px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Flowers are made on the side of figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D23.png&quot; style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px; width: 81px; height: 100px;&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/F1_Madhuri_Railways_06.07.2022_D24.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 17px; height: 22px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flowers are made on the vertex of the figure.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Vertex:-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;A point where two or more line segments meet and the point of intersection of edges called Vertex.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Sides:-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;The side can be defined as the line segment that joins two vertices in a shape or two dimensional figure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>অনুসৃত যুক্তিটি হলো:</p>

<ol>
